     definition ~ biid is used as an antecedent, however, any true wff, such as
     an axiom, can be used in its place.  (Contributed by Anthony Hart,
     13-Oct-2010.) $)
  df-tru $a |- ( T. <-> ( ph <-> ph ) ) $.

