     (Contributed by NM, 5-Aug-1993.) $)
  ax-14 $a |- ( x = y -> ( z e. x -> z e. y ) ) $.

  $( Lemma used in proofs of substitution properties.  (Contributed by NM,
     5-Aug-1993.) $)
  equs3 $p |- ( E. x ( x = y /\ ph ) <-> -. A. x ( x = y -> -. ph ) ) $=
